Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《指定幸存者》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on "Designated Survivor"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会大厦受到袭击  总统死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Capitol's been attacked. Eagle is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-整个国会  内阁  -天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Congress, the Cabinet. - Oh, oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  你现在是美国总统了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, you are now the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚有些坏人做了一些坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some bad people did something bad tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸的职责就是确保我们都安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it's Dad's job to make sure we're all safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟国务卿柯克曼的手下一起工作三年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been with Secretary Kirkman's staff for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是柯克曼总统了  而且你并没得到授权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's President Kirkman now, and you're not authorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知不知道始作俑者是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do we know - who's responsible for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在下定论还为时尚早\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still too early to determine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得给大家一个交代\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got to give them something,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在全世界都在关注我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the whole world is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在让住房和城市发展部长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have a Housing and Urban Development Secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌管着美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}running the free world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的可是除掉在位总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're talking about removing a sitting president.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这里有发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got something over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了  是颗哑弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's clear. Bomb's a dud.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没完事之前  不会居功吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't take credit for something until you're done, right?
