Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was no chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜  我知道没有消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah, I understand there was no chatter,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们仍需要核查所有可能的嫌犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we still need to check all of the usual suspects --
