Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  拉出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, pull that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国民众们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My fellow Americans,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚  我们遭遇了恐怖袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tonight our way of life came under attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}早间新闻  柯克曼总统发表第一次讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不法分子试图用这种怯懦的行为削弱我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This act of cowardice was meant to cripple our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一如以往  美国将向全世界展示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But as before, America will show the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会被恐惧压垮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we will not bow down to fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将狠狠还击  坚定地走下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we will fight back, that we will persevere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是汤姆·柯克曼总统第一次对全国发表讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this was President Tom Kirkman's first address to the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在两小时前  他才匆匆宣誓就任总统一职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It came just two hours after he was unceremoniously sworn in as our new president.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}早间新闻  柯克曼总统的第一次讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幸的是  昨晚的讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately, last night's speech
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有缓和公众紧绷的神经\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}did little to calm the frayed nerves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说演讲内容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Words aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯克曼之前是住房和城市发展部长  未经选举\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kirkman is an unelected, untested HUD secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}柯克曼是正确的人选吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而如今全世界都需要领导力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at a time where the world is looking for leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会大厦的遗骸...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14} ...remains of the Capitol,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力搜救幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}searching for both survivors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}国会山的搜索仍在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为全国人民都关注的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and answers to the questions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all Americans are asking --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did this happen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还安全吗...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and will life ever be the sa--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-早安  总统先生  -早上好  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Morning, Mr. President. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西侧  在右边还是左边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}West Wing, right or left?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边走  在右手边  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way, to the right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤凰[总统]出发了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phoenix on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子今天不想让我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My wife didn't want me to come in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她担心白宫就是下一个目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's afraid the White House is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨晚本该过去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was supposed to go last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没找到保姆就没去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I couldn't get a sitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}头条新闻  国会大厦致命爆炸案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅丽莎死了  大家都死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Melissa's dead, everyone's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-亚伦  -早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Aaron. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-大家在总统办公室等着向您汇报  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We have a briefing waiting for you in the Oval, sir. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-总统先生  -怀特  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mr. President. - Wyatt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  先生  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, sir. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  我提醒一下您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, I just have to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可能会比您之前更加紧张和忙碌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This might be a bit more hectic than you're used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白  应该能搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I understand. I think we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经加强了油气管道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've added increased security to our oil and gas pipelines,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电网  炼油厂  化工储罐的安全戒备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}power grids, refineries, chemical storage tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公众交通依然要保持关闭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mass transit is still on lock down --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞机  火车等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}planes and trains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然要禁止外来移民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Immigration remains frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  请您授权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, you have to authorize
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们立即关闭银行  -不  不能关银行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- we close the banks immediately. - No, we can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能阻止民众支取自己的财产\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We cannot keep the American people from their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,48小时取不了钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}48 hours without Bank of America
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总比48个月经济萧条强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is better than a 48-month depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果所有人都同时提款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If everyone withdraws their money at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银行会破产\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the banks will collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸弹的事调查得怎样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are we at with the bombing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚特伍德副局长很快会来汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deputy Director Atwood will be briefing us soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们排查了有能力和资金制造此次爆炸案的组织\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we're looking at groups with the skills and resources to do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黎巴嫩真主党  基地组织  朝鲜  三原党\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hezbollah, Al-Qaeda, North Korea, RGB.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密歇根州的暴力事件是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, what's this about violence in Michigan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们收到报告  迪尔伯恩市发生突发事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're getting reports of flare-ups in Dearborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警方认为是当地的穆斯林群体所为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Police targeting the local Muslim community.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想知道的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but what I want to know is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子是如何将爆炸物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how did the terrorists bring explosives
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功带进国会大厦的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}into the Capitol Building in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're working on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时  我们要想尽一切办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, we have to go after everyone we suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追踪所有嫌疑人  和他们的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We go after them, after their families any way we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  你是在提议动用私刑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. Are you talking about enhanced interrogation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们毁掉了国会大厦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They destroyed our Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该采取一切必要措施\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm saying we do whatever we have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以打扰一下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I just get a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  能不能一次只关注一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody, why don't we just focus on one thing at a time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  你能让我静一静吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, can you just give me a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}住房与城市发展部部长专座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}总统专座
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}总统专座
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想自己静一静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just needed to find somewhere quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  那边有点太吵闹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, admittedly, it got a little loud in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵闹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球赛可以吵闹  亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A Caps game is loud, Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在总统办公室里  那就是混乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back there in the Oval Office, that was chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要秩序和制度  否则将一事无成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need order, a system, or this is never gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要让美国政府重新运作起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to get this government up and running.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要尽快组建内阁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We... We need a cabinet and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a good idea, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首要任务是提名您的幕僚长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but first order of business is going to be naming your Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认真的吗  这么快就开始玩手段了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seriously? You're making a play right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没决定好选谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not ready to make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你们两人同心协力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I need is both of you to step up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助我组建内阁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and help me put together a cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me you can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-可以  总统先生  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, Mr. President. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要暂时关闭银行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For now, we're gonna close the banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但自动提款机和信用卡依然能用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ATMs and credit will still be available.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你们严密监控密歇根州的局势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to monitor the situation in Michigan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要加快爆炸事件的调查进度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I want you to keep me up to speed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且及时向我汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the investigation into the bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全国人民都想知道是谁干的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The American people want to know who did this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我也是  -知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- and so do I. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍后我要去察看国会大厦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Later today, I want to see the Capitol Building,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会大厦遗址\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or what's left of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您确定要在这个节骨眼去吗  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure that's a... good idea right now, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  您就应该现在去  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no. Th--that -- that's exactly what you need, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次公关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A do-over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚的演讲没有缓解国民的紧张情绪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}L-Last night's speech didn't exactly put minds at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总统亲自去现场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you, sir, at the site...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以传达一个信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}now that sends a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-表现出...  -默哀  亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It shows a... - Respect, Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了默哀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it shows respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在做秀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a photo-op.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-听您安排  先生  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Whatever you say, sir. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去工作吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}政府大楼成为废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  站着别动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir. Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  怎么了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Morning, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-背包里装的是什么  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's in the backpack? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的背包里装着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your backpack... what's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是些工作上的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, just my stuff for, uh, work...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-文件之类的  -你在哪里工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Papers and stuff. - Where do you work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在白宫工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I work at the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  在白宫吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really? The White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  总统休息的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, you know, where the President sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来这一套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You being a wise ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道为什么你们要拦我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to know why you stopped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是先上报住址  拿出身份证来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you tell us where you live and show us some I.D. First.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就住在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I live right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又冷又窄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's cold and it's cramped,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可以走路去健身房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I can walk to my gym,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也还不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I got that going for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛斯·怀特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth Wright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的真名吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}According to my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keith.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的身份没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢合作  怀特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for your cooperation, Mr. Wright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得挂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉妈妈我爱她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell Mom I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内阁成员候选人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, cabinet members.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布兰查德怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about Blanchard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当州议员吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For State?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他任副职三年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's qualified-- three years as deputy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还有两个私密的脸书账号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He also has two secret Facebook accounts
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且对照看他小孩的女孩子们颇有兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and an affinity for the coeds who look after his kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得加菲尔德合适\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm thinking Garfield's our guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  再想想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, think again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在国会山树敌太多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's made more than a few enemies on the Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽  我不想打击你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emily, I hate to break it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但国会山已经不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but there is no Hill anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会山已经不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no Hill anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密歇根出事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something happened in Michigan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必一看见我就起身敬礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't need to get up every time I walk into a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  您一点也不像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, sir. Virtually no resemblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉打扰你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我其实是来道歉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-- I actually came in to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚你为我写了一篇非常棒的演讲稿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last night, you wrote me a home run of a speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天早上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新闻界似乎更希望让其他人来念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it seems like the press wished anybody else delivered it but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许国民只是还没有准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe the country's just not ready, yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去齐心协力拥护谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to come together behind anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕你有着世界一流的演讲稿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even with the best speech in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事情需要跟您汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's something you need to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警方在穆斯林社区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Police imposing a curfew
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}特大事件  密歇根州迪尔伯恩市  全城宵禁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大肆实施宵禁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on predominantly Muslim neighborhoods
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并勒令居民必须服从  否则将被拘捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and ordering residents to obey it or face arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些公民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These are citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并未受到任何犯罪指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who have not been charged with any crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因为信仰就遭遇如此对待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who are simply targeted because of their religious beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国公民自由联盟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The American Civil Liberties Union
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公开谴责迪尔伯恩警方的这一行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}denounced the actions by Dearborn police
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-侵害了...  -总统先生  准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- as a violation of an individual's... - Mr. President, we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公民基本权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...basic civil rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但考虑到国会大厦遭遇了恐怖袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But in the wake of the attack on the Capitol,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说这才是我国急需的监管方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some are saying this is just the type of policing this country needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-州长叫什么  -罗伊斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Governor...? - Royce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊斯州长  你好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor Royce, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, about as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以想象  很多事情需要整顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a lot to manage here, as you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我想帮助你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, and I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了新闻  迪尔伯恩的警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen reports - that the police in Dearborn
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在围捕穆斯林社区的居民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are rounding up members of the Muslim community.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢好意  我知道这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir. Yes, I'm aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以帮你制止那些警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, like I said, we'd like to help you stop the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要制止他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would I stop the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是在执行我的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're acting on my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你的命令  -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Your orders? - That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你是否了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know if you know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这里是穆斯林人口最多的市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I have the largest Muslim population in the country, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不代表他们就会犯法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That doesn't mean they're doing anything wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会变成激进分子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or that they've been radicalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  但我敢肯定他们知道内情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, but I'm willing to bet they know someone who is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,州长  你不能因为单纯的恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor, you can't target an innocent population
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就伤害无辜大众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because you're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你有责任  -我对所有公民都有责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You have a responsibility-- - To all my citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的首要职责是保障他们的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my first and only priority is to make sure they're safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something that Washington--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华盛顿  或者说曾经的政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if-- if there even is such a place anymore--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎并没有做到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has proven incapable of doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,州长  联邦政府...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor, the federal government--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚被彻底击垮了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...Was effectively snuffed out last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会没了  最高法院也没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no Congress, there is no Supreme Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在密歇根公民的问题上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When it comes to the people of Michigan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是最高权威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am the highest authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无权命令我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you have none over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言  我现在是国家总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With all due respect, sir, I am the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需跟我浪费口舌了  柯克曼先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so you'll have to excuse me, Mr. Kirkman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先慢慢学习如何当总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}While you're busy learning how to become President,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有一千万公民要保护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got 10 million citizens to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,州长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊斯州长  听得到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor Royce? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  知道世界各国元首\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, you should know that messages of support
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在接连不断发来支持贺电\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}continue to pour in from heads of state around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该看看哪些需要由您亲自回复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should go over which calls you want to return personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都亲自回吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would think all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概有多少来电\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many calls are we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一共175通  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About 175, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还是排下先后顺序吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we should prioritize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟您说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to know that I don't care
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在意那些所谓的专家们怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what the so-called pundits are saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您昨晚的发言让我十分感动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was very moved by your words last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  请问你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me, but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  这是女议员金布尔·霍斯拉滕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, this is congresswoman Kimble Hookstraten.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congresswoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是另一位指定幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I was last night's other designated survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一位...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Other designated...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请借一步说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse us, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两个指定幸存者吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are - two designated survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  共和党也选出了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, the Republicans chose someone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位发表国情咨文演说的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to sit out of - the State of the Union, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保障他们的权益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So they'd be represented.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道多少关于霍斯拉滕的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, what do you know about Hookstraten?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾经就职于参议员凯雷旗下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, you were - on Senator Carlyle's staff
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都在众议院筹款委员会  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when they were both on Ways and Means, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-跟踪狂  -说正经的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Stalker. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很聪明  非常聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's smart. Very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三代华盛顿特区贵族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Third-generation D.C. blue blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从政九年  共和党纪律委员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}nine years, Republican whip,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对政坛所有人都了如指掌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}knows every detail about every player in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  她比现任总统有经验得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're saying - she's a lot more experienced than the President?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  我们去给罗伊斯州长打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Let's go get Governor Royce on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,435名代表  100名参议员和9名法官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}435 representatives, 100 senators, and 9 justices.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只剩下我们两个了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now it's just down to the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解  都不知道该悔恨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. You don't know whether to feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是该庆幸自己活了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ashamed or grateful to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apologetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向被迫接受我作为领导人的美国公民道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To the American people for being stuck with me as their leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直面现实吧  专家们说得很有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, let's face it. The pundits might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道我今天早上做了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what I did this morning, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哭泣并祈祷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cried and then I prayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我上次这样是什么时候吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know when the last time I did those two things together was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9.11的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}9.11?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候没人认为我们能挺过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody thought we could get through it back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们做到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也没人认为我们能坚持下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And nobody thinks - we can get through it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在白宫属于你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is your house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情发挥你的才能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So make it your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要什么  尽管提出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever you need, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共和党  民主党还是无党派人士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Republican, Democrat, Independent
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不重要了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们都是美国人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all Americans today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  女议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, congresswoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我金布尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kimble, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布尔  今天下午晚些时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kimble, later this afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去国会现场感谢急救先遣队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to the Capitol site to thank the first responders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们两个人一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it would be a nice show of unity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让民众看到政府的团结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if we were to do that together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd be honored, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗尼  那是未爆炸的炸弹吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ronnie, is that the unexploded munition?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么进展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's it telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是俄罗斯反坦克雷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Russian anti-tank mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可能是从阿富汗战区得到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}likely pulled from the ground in Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内核是被拆过的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The guts are cannibalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面是斯拉夫产的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cyrillic on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密封环却是巴基斯坦的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the lock ring is Pakistani,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞针更加新一点  很可能来自伊朗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the firing pin is newer, probably Iranian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和圣战恐怖组织\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that is consistent with what we've seen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手里的地雷是一样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from some Jihadist terror groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到其他炸弹的检测结果之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we should be able to point the finger directly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该知道谁是始作俑者了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when we get the lab results from the other bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  但是这一枚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, but this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这一枚没有爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why didn't this one go off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any number of reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯的红线和伊朗的绿线不搭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Russian red wire to Iranian green doesn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主爆炸物降解了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the main charge degraded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也不排除人为原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I wouldn't rule out good old-fashioned human error.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这些幕后真凶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're telling me that the people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一举炸毁美国首都之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who blew up our U.S. Capitol in one shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有测试触发器和接线吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}didn't test the triggers, the wiring?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then what are you suggesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许这枚炸弹本来就不会爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if this bomb - wasn't meant to explode?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶手只是希望我们找到它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if it was meant to be found?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管州长在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I don't care - what the Governor's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国总统要跟他讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The President of the United Sates needs to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是请求  这是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I'm not -- I'm not asking you. I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让我等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not -- I'm not gonna hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万万没想到  有资格担任总检察长的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd think - there would be more people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然这么少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}qualified for Attorney General.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该说什么好呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell am I supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在自言自语吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this a writer thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望通过柯克曼的现场讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to find a way to unite us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让美国民众团结起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at Kirkman's remarks at the rubble,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但密歇根可能只是个开端\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but Michigan is probably just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界正在分崩离析\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The world is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就不要写在讲话稿里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably don't want to put that in the speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我还在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God, it's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温布兰特不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like Wynbrandt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他晚上去上城市学院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He went to city college at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读法律系  非常顾家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}law school, good family man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅西比较合适\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Massey's our guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为托马斯工作过  耶鲁毕业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He clerked for Thomas, he went to Yale,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是法律杂志的编辑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}editor of the Law Journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是写在纸上给你看的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all about what's on paper for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听过温布兰特讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard Wynbrandt speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有正确的价值观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The man has good values.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽  密歇根州州长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emily, the Governor of Michigan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本宣称密歇根州要独立了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is basically declaring his state a sovereign nation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没时间讨论价值观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so we don't have time for values.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也不能写进讲话里  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I probably shouldn't put that in the speech either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊斯州长这么说的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor Royce said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他是最高权威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That he's the highest authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么说的  而且斩钉截铁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what he said -- and in no uncertain terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说完就挂了我的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then he hung the phone up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不能这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, - he doesn't get to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有宪法赋予的义务...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has a constitutional obligation --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不明白吗  艾丽克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you get it, Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊斯想要撕毁宪法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Royce wants - to tear up the Constitution,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不仅是他一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he's not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能让他这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you can't let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  我不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust me, I'm not going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总检察长办公室的几位律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got some lawyers coming over
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经在过来的路上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from the Attorney General's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会弄清楚可以用哪些法律手段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll figure out - what our legal options are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会处理好这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we're handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和邓肯联系过了  法院都关闭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I spoke to Duncan. The courts are closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市场  银行  学校  机场  都关闭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Markets, banks, schools, airports, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公司里一半的初级助理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half the junior associates in the firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在考虑离开华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're thinking of leaving Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩妮怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's Penny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得她能想清楚发生了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think she even understands what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只知道我们现在住在白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Besides the fact that we now live in the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她爸爸成了总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}her father is the President,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有她睡在一张很大的床上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she's sleeping in a very big bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余都不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直努力让她不看电视\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been trying to keep her away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李奥呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他整天都在房间里  关着门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's been in his room all day, with the door shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本和他往常一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, basically being Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我们能不能  就五分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you think we could, for five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假装这一切没有发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just pretend that - this isn't really happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这总统办公室里有点困难啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kind of hard to do in the Oval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  先生  我说了你在忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, sir. I told him you were busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事  将军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can I help you, General?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我们有些事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid that's something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要私下商量一下  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have to discuss in private, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是我妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh. This is my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的妻子没有最高权限  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your wife does not have code-word clearance, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和联邦调查局副局长亚特伍德联系了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just spoke to - FBI Deputy Director Atwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验室鉴定结果出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The lab results came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经确定了爆炸物的来源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They've made a positive I.D. on the explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道是谁炸了国会大厦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know - who blew up the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔萨卡喜欢大规模伤亡袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Al-Sakar likes mass-casuality attacks --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在马尼拉埋下氯气罐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a chlorine storage tank in Manila,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把沙林毒气罐投掷到内罗比军事基地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sarin gas tanks lobbed onto our military base in Nairobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局爆炸装置中心的初步分析显示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Preliminary analysis from the FBI's Explosive Device Center
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在国会大厦废墟发现的碎片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tells us that residue found on the Capitol debris
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和艾尔萨卡使用过的炸弹一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is consistent with bombs used by Al-Sakar in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府可以公开宣布艾尔萨卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's time to publicly name Al-Sakar
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这次犯罪行为的始作俑者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as the perpetrator of this crime
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且采取相应的行动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and take appropriate action.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在采取任何行动之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Before we do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦调查局是否确信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the FBI is absolutely certain
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾尔萨卡制造了这场袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Al-Sakar was behind the attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,75%确信  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}75%, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,75%吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}75%?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于这样的任务来说已经很高了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's as high as it gets when it comes to a call like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,75%在考试中只能得C  将军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}75% is still a "C" On a test, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是考试  这是战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not a test. This is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就更应该查得准确一些  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the more reason to get it right, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:20:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  我知道我们曾有过摩擦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, I know we got off on the wrong foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨晚幸运地躲过了伊朗人的袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You did a fine job staving off the Iranians last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我提醒你这个国家现在命悬一线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I am advising you that the country is on the brink,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话解决不了问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and talk will not work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国急需行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}America is demanding action
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我现在给了你一个我们要消灭的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I am giving you an enemy we can kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我不想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I don't want to strike back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给凶手一记反击吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}against the people who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了同事  朋友  我爱的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lost colleagues, friends, people I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要找出从计划到执行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to find every single person
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次袭击的每一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}involved in this attack from planning to execution
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将他们碎尸万段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and rip them limb from limb,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我得确切地知道到底是谁做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is why I need to know exactly who did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过75%再来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come back to me with more than 75%,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时我亲自发射导弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I'll launch the damn missiles myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还需要多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,25%啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}25%, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,截至三十分钟前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The death toll as of 30 minutes ago
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡人数超过九百人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is 900 plus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括总统  副总统  内阁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That includes the President, Vice President, Cabinet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已确认身份的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}those we've been able to I.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会及最高法院职员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from Congress and the Supreme Court...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局局长雅各布也确认死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and FBI Director Jacobs is also confirmed dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前推测是艾尔萨卡所为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The working theory is, this is the work of Al-Sakar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道他们是基地组织最新的分支\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So as we know, this is the latest offshoot of Al-Qaeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们散布在整个北非地区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are dispersed throughout North Africa,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常难以追踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which makes them very, very hard to track.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们得随机应变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we need to be crafty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要调集我们所有的资源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to reach out to your sources,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不计成本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}spread some cash around,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽一切努力搜寻线索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do whatever you have to do to firm up that link.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人宣称负责吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔萨卡宣称对此事负责了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is Al-Sakar taking credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, they haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当年本·拉登过了几个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it was months before Bin Laden
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才宣称对袭击双子塔的事负责  所以...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}took responsibility for the Towers, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟别人一样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Same as everyone else, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚从安德鲁斯那过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just came from Andrews.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们发现的未引爆爆炸物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bomb we just found, the UXO,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能跟你所想的不太一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it may not be telling you what you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来听听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, I'll bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.25,0:21:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  如果他们就想让我们找到这个呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, well, what if they wanted us to find it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好让我们把注意力集中在艾尔萨卡上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that we would look at Al-Sakar
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忽视其他可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and not consider any other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的推测有证据支持吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you back up your theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,09年在伊拉克我的推测很准\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, my theories were good enough for you in '09 in Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不一样  汉娜  你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is different, Hannah, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且我已经跟科克兰将军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Besides, I've already talked to General Cochrane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和联席会议打过招呼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the Joint Chiefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你还是得跟总统报告的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're still gonna brief the President later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好把各方推测都说一下  你觉得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Best to give them all the theories, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那如果不是艾尔萨卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So if it wasn't Al-Sakar,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁炸了国会大厦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who blew up the Capitol Building?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不知道  这才是我最害怕的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know yet, and that's what scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.55,0:22:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  麦克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, w-what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要微笑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I supposed to smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到时候大概会想哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I'll probably feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.38,0:22:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-做你自己就好  -我知道  只是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just be yourself. - I know, I just --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让你失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让这个国家失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to let the country down,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌他们给我选的这件衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I hate this that they picked it out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧  我就像个白宫里的沙发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look. I look like the White House sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你里面还要穿这个的  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's to fit over this, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克  这些东西有必要吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mike, is this all really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统及其家人有两种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two ways the President and his family
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开白宫的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can leave the White House --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.98,0:22:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么身穿防弹背心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}out the front door in Kevlar vests
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随13辆装甲车车队从前门出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a 13-car armored motorcade
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么戴顶棒球帽坐轿车从后门出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or out the back in a Chevy and a ball cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me the coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小豌豆  还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, little pea, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是怕我摔跤保护我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is just to protect me in case I fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害的是  你打我我不会痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cool thing is you can punch it, and I won't feel a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来试试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on, try.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.65,0:23:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-到时间了  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's time, sir. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  李奥哪去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}H-H-Hold on. W-Where's Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别紧张  妈  我在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Relax, Mom, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  你看好你妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, you need to watch your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让她看电视  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And keep her away from the TV, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新闻太过真实了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any of the news, it's too real.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不需要看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She doesn't need to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  你不系领带吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, you won't be wearing a tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是正式场合  亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a formal occasion, Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ok. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤凰准备好了正在路上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phoenix is ready and on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.76,0:23:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克  只是好奇  之前是什么  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mike, just out of curiosity, what was it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当住房和城市发展部部长时的代号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My code name when I was Secretary of HUD,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼镜  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Glasses," Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.14,0:24:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三小时前给州长留言了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We left word for the Governor three hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.57,0:24:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  请再和他说一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, p-please tell him, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.47,0:24:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管政界的人了  他们一向粗鲁无礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forget politics, it's just plain rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们到底怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, what the hell's wrong with people anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.05,0:24:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们很害怕  亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People are scared, Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.55,0:24:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会过去一直是力量的象征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Capitol used to be a symbol of strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在变成了一堆灰烬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and now it's a pile of ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.11,0:24:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认识的人都不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And everyone we know is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.82,0:24:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以想想今天  每一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would think today, of all days,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.02,0:24:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们至少能够假装是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}people could at least pretend to be decent human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.70,0:24:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么这么惊讶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.87,0:24:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾难让人们既感激又害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tragedy either makes people appreciate their fellow men,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.38,0:24:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的同伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or fear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.01,0:24:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,州长也不例外  他只是被选出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Governor's no different. He's just elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.77,0:24:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你能和我一起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.96,0:24:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.13,0:24:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.12,0:24:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天  我还被要求卸任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yesterday, I was asked to resign,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.68,0:25:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在聊搬去蒙特利尔的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we were talking about moving to Montreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.04,0:25:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我却在试着让整个美国政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I'm trying to put the entire U.S. Government
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.85,0:25:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凝聚起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}back together
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.25,0:25:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止这个国家分裂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and stop the country from tearing itself apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.46,0:25:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱般的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hell of a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.50,0:25:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.62,0:25:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统的车队来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the President's motorcade coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.56,0:25:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.99,0:25:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you ready for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.64,0:25:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能有人准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can anybody be ready for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.91,0:25:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  专心工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, hold the work. Hold the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.37,0:26:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.34,0:26:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.87,0:26:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.53,0:26:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.39,0:26:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.29,0:26:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是杰森·阿特伍德  副局长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Jason Atwood, Deputy Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.16,0:26:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-里面为您准备好了一份简报  先生  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We got a briefing ready for you inside, sir. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖爆炸装置分析中心的初步分析\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prelim analysis from TEDAC
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.12,0:26:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表明残骸上找到的的爆炸残渣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}indicates that the explosive residue found on
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.43,0:26:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑索今  也被叫做旋风炸药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the debris is called cyclonite, also known as RDX.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.97,0:26:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为它和塑化剂混合在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We believe it was mixed with a plasticizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.63,0:26:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样能使破坏力达到最大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's - what maximizes the destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.44,0:26:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让房子自己倒塌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}allowed the chamber to come down on itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.24,0:26:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.93,0:26:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔萨卡已经开始使用黑索今了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Al-Sakar has access to RDX?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.12,0:26:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的长官  这是他们最拿手的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. It's their signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.26,0:27:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们找到的装置呢  炸弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about the device you found -- the bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.52,0:27:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它为什么没爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why didn't it go off?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.55,0:27:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为是人为失误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We believe it was human error.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.21,0:27:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还在进行一些试验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're still running some tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.85,0:27:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢  副局长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Thank you, Deputy Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.52,0:27:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.80,0:27:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会向您实时通报的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll keep you updated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.69,0:27:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克  拿着我的外套  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mike, take my coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.78,0:27:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我需要您穿上外套  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, I'm gonna need you to keep that vest on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.70,0:27:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克  我们来这是为了建立信心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mike, we're here to project confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.75,0:27:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件外套能够帮你重建信心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does this vest project confidence to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.53,0:27:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.65,0:27:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我赢了  -你作弊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I win. - You cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.91,0:27:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我知道你的把戏  小姑娘  -我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I know your game, little girl. - I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.37,0:27:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I got to take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.68,0:27:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该照看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're supposed to watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.15,0:27:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是白宫打来的  佩妮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the White House, Penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.84,0:27:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确定你很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.02,0:28:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于新任总统柯克曼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A truly somber moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.22,0:28:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来说是一个沉重的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as newly sworn-in President Kirkman
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.95,0:28:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他于今日亲临\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}makes his first visit
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.64,0:28:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了恐怖袭击现场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the site of the terrorist attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.67,0:28:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拭目以待他对公众的解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will stand by for his comments to the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.10,0:28:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多照相机  亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot of cameras, Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.47,0:28:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为您是总统  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are the President, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.25,0:28:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下  那个可以借给我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me. Could I borrow that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.12,0:28:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给您 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.38,0:28:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-按这里吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just press here? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.45,0:28:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好  我叫汤姆·柯克曼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, my name is Tom Kirkman.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.85,0:28:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概昨晚十点半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last night at approximately 10:30 p.m.,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.83,0:28:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宣誓就职美国总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was sworn in as President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.39,0:28:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've come down here
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.13,0:28:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了感谢你们每一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I wanted to thank each and every one of you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.90,0:28:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你们在这里所做的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the work that you're doing here
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.13,0:28:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们知道美国在哀悼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and let you know that America mourns.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.55,0:28:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.92,0:28:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是疯狂的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was an act of madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.74,0:28:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是恐怖行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was an act of terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.75,0:29:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天  我们见到了人性最坏的一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yesterday, we saw the worst in humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.60,0:29:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天  我见到了最好的一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today, I see it's best.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.73,0:29:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你们都很累  很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you're all tired, scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.45,0:29:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你们想知道真相  想知道凶手是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you want answers, someone to blame,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.53,0:29:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该找谁算账\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}someone to fight against.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.79,0:29:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你们要知道我也是这么想的  -怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I need you to know that I want that, too. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.61,0:29:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even, though, today,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.35,0:29:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-看上去我们像是失败了  -密歇根州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- it might look as though we've fallen... - It's Michigan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.77,0:29:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你们保证我们会再次崛起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise you we will rise again
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.72,0:29:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}密歇根州  迪尔伯恩\N警察袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.13,0:29:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且会更好更强大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}better and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.26,0:29:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所失去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those who we've lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.55,0:29:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是国家的领导人  亲人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are leaders, family members...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.68,0:29:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及我们所爱的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.14,0:29:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你们发誓  他们绝不会白白死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I swear to you, they will not have died in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.00,0:29:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看密歇根州怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you see what's going on in Michigan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.17,0:29:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时此刻我们所在的这个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This place where we stand right here, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.28,0:29:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将永远都是神圣的土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will forever be hallowed ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.63,0:29:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们必须\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we must always...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.62,0:29:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远铭记这里的人们所付出的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}respect the incredible sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.77,0:29:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that was made here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.79,0:29:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  你对发生在迪尔伯恩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, do you have anything to say
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.06,0:29:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察殴打一名穆斯林青年的事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about the Muslim teenager in Dearborn
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.63,0:29:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么要说的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who was beaten by police?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.60,0:29:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统现在不接受任何提问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The President's not answering any questions right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.48,0:29:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -没有要回应的吗  柯克曼总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - You have no response, President Kirkman?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.36,0:29:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我没听清问题  -那个被警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I-I didn't hear the question. - The Muslim teenager
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.84,0:30:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殴打的穆斯林青年  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who was beaten by police, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.28,0:30:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你有什么要说的吗  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you have a comment? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.03,0:30:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是否担心人权正在被侵犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you concerned that their civil rights are being violated?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.25,0:30:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宫方面是否担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is the White House concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.26,0:30:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对穆斯林群体的暴力会升级\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about escalating violence against Muslims?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.89,0:30:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会让美国人挨打吗  柯克曼先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you gonna let Americans get beaten, Mr. Kirkman.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.00,0:30:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手拿出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Show me your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.92,0:30:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把手拿出来  -我没做错什么  别碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Show me your hands! - I didn't do anything wrong. Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.54,0:30:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有枪  有枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gun! Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.07,0:30:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩护  撤离到车上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cover and evacuate to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.54,0:30:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰他  他什么都没做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get your hands off him. He's not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.79,0:30:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是部手机  是部手机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a phone. It's a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.85,0:30:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤凰在我这  重复  凤凰在我这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have Phoenix! I repeat, I have Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.79,0:30:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后退  后退\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back up! Back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.34,0:30:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后退\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.51,0:30:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走走走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.85,0:30:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上给我联系罗伊斯州长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get me Governor Royce on the phone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.43,0:30:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直在联系  他不接电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been trying. He won't take the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.74,0:30:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫他不接电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean he won't take the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.67,0:30:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道那个孩子的情况吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do we know anything about the condition of the boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.49,0:30:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密歇根州那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the one in the Michigan?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.65,0:30:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他内出血  正在手术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's in surgery with internal bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.35,0:30:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  他知道我们在找他  可他不管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knows we're calling, sir. He doesn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.99,0:30:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟总检察长办公室的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to talk to a couple lawyers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.06,0:30:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几个律师谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from the Attorney General's Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.02,0:30:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.83,0:31:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-丹尼·法耶德  夫人  -他多大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Danny Fayad, ma'am. - How old is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.75,0:31:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有几个总检察长的候选人可能会帮上忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have a couple A.G. candidates who could be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.76,0:31:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫他们过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.38,0:31:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰你  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry to bother you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.24,0:31:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你女儿在楼上要找你  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Your daughter needs you upstairs. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.22,0:31:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆  那个男孩  他17岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom, the boy... he's 17 --
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.89,0:31:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和李奥同岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The same age as Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.11,0:31:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩妮要找我  我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Penny needs me. I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.23,0:31:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要跟你解释什么  汉娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have to explain myself to you Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.01,0:31:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向总统说的是我认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gave the President what I determined
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.31,0:31:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最直接相关的情报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was the most relevant intel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.07,0:31:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉他的正是这起事件的凶手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or you gave him what the group who did this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.95,0:31:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要你告诉他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}wanted you to give him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.88,0:31:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他没有掌握全部情况他怎么领导我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can he lead if he doesn't have all the facts?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.61,0:31:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你把全部情况告诉我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you should have given them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.23,0:31:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.60,0:31:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是不相信你  或者不想相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I don't belive you, or that I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.14,0:31:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人炸掉了国会大厦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone blew up the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.31,0:31:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道还会发生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who knows what's possible anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.97,0:31:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外  现在掌权的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On top of that, we got a guy in office
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.50,0:31:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是排在继承顺序的第十一位那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who's number 11 in the line of succession.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.91,0:31:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在不能向他汇报推测出来的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't go to him with speculation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.57,0:31:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  如果你想让我跟他说你的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, if you want me to go back to him with your theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.96,0:31:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请拿出证据来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}please prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.65,0:31:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密歇根州的情况已经失控了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The situation in Michigan is out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.67,0:32:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个青年现在情况很危急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now we've got a teenager in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.84,0:32:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要知道在法律层面我有哪些选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to know what my legal options are right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.58,0:32:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.40,0:32:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以使用最高条款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can invoke the Supremacy Clause,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.53,0:32:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发布一条行政命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}issue an executive order
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.97,0:32:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让罗伊斯州长命令他那里的警察停手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}saying Governor Royce must force his police to stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.24,0:32:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个办法不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a bad call.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.18,0:32:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发布行政命令会被别人认为很不友好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}E.O.S can be perceived as very hostile.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.28,0:32:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你有什么建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then what would you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.50,0:32:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统宣言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A Presidential Proclamation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.88,0:32:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这没有实质意义  只是象征性的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is nothing more than a symbolic empty gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.90,0:32:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让人觉得很软弱  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It -- it looks weak, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.08,0:32:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布什总统在卡特里娜飓风后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bush used a Proclamation
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.35,0:32:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过发布总统宣言来保护了灾区的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to secure disaster areas after Katrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.35,0:32:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这可不是个没有实质意义的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That hardly seems like an empty gesture to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.44,0:32:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不建议把发布戒严令排除在外  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't take declaring Martial Law off the table either, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.95,0:32:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想成为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want this to be
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.89,0:32:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史上在位最短的总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the shortest presidency in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.77,0:32:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就直说了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.18,0:32:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行政命令会被视为敌对恶意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An executive order will be perceived as too hostile,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.75,0:32:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统宣言势单力孤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a Presidential Proclamation -- too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.04,0:32:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒严令也许非常明智\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Martial Law -- either very, very smart
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.67,0:32:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许具有巨大的自我摧残性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or incredibly self-destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.91,0:32:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位  我来问你们一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guys, let me ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.25,0:32:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底会不会同意我的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you agree on anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.87,0:32:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-会  -不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes. - Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.27,0:32:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.15,0:32:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.94,0:33:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, how do you think she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.04,0:33:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她刚刚看到自己的爸爸差点被人踩死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She just watched her father almost get trampled.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.71,0:33:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我交给你一个任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You had one job --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.32,0:33:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不让她看电视  -我照做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- to keep her away from the TV. - I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.93,0:33:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来你没做到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.27,0:33:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把她一个人丢在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Y-You left her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.65,0:33:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有电话要接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.15,0:33:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照看她不是我的责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It-it's not my job to be her parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.82,0:33:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, guess what.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.41,0:33:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今时不同往日了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all doing jobs that we weren't doing yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.93,0:33:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李奥  我们的生活发生了巨变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leo, nothing's the same anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.32,0:33:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这个要求很过分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I know it's asking a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.62,0:33:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你得快点成长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're just gonna have to grow up faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.17,0:33:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前相比  我有更多的事要指望你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I'm gonna need to count on you in more ways than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.93,0:33:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.51,0:33:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.73,0:33:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guess we'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.42,0:33:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这些文件带去财政部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take these to Treasury.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.32,0:33:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们我会亲自签署命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell them Social Security checks will keep going out,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.37,0:33:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-社会保障金会继续发放  -是  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- if I have to sign them myself. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.40,0:33:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦  我们不是已经达成共识了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aaron, I thought we were in agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.34,0:33:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的吗  将军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really, General?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.61,0:33:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达成什么共识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.51,0:34:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他手足无措  力所不及\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's in over his head, out of his depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.20,0:34:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要说服你的新上司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to convince your new boss
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.46,0:34:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔-萨卡就是爆炸事件的罪魁祸首\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Al-Sakar is behind the bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.06,0:34:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是说得很清楚了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he was pretty clear in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.34,0:34:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在确定之前  他不会乱任命官职的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until he's certain, he will not name anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.83,0:34:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得  说服他是你的职责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And as I recall, it's your job to convince him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.21,0:34:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-亚伦  你是幕僚长  -其实我不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Aaron, you're Chief of Staff. - Actually, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.12,0:34:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那谁才是  -他还没任命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So, who is? - He hasn't named one, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.59,0:34:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又在犹豫不决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet another trigger he won't pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.31,0:34:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看书吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Light reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.87,0:34:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可惜  看来维基百科\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, sadly, it seems that Wikipedia
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.86,0:34:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宪法理论方面的资料有些单薄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is a little thin on constitutional-law theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.45,0:34:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于密歇根州事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, did the lawyers
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.19,0:34:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,律师团没想出解决办法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not give you any answers about Michigan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.11,0:34:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想出了一堆办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They gave me plenty of answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.20,0:34:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是都不适用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They just weren't the right ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.92,0:34:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是最重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't even matter, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.61,0:34:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法和罗伊斯州长通电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't get Governor Royce back on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.37,0:34:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是时候对他采取强硬的态度了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, maybe it's time to force his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.19,0:34:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.61,0:34:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当年乔治·华莱士拒绝服从\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When George Wallace refused an order
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.01,0:34:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合并阿拉巴马州学校的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to integrate schools in Alabama,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.43,0:35:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰·肯尼迪让他的兄弟联合国民警卫队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}J.F.K. had his brother federalize the National Guard
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.82,0:35:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫使他遵守法律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and forced him to obey the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.01,0:35:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联合国民警卫队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Federalize the National Guard."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.30,0:35:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪明的点子  但却有些...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's brilliant, but it's also a little --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.61,0:35:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nuclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.94,0:35:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.56,0:35:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要暴力的解决方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't need a nuclear solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.37,0:35:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要用政治手段来解决问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need a political one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.84,0:35:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好在我们家里有一位政治家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good thing we have - a politician in the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.63,0:35:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时再看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.56,0:35:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  一号线有您的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, your call's on line 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.24,0:35:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.53,0:35:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  非常感谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.51,0:35:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.74,0:35:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-密歇根州的那个孩子  -丹尼·法亚德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The boy from Michigan. - Danny Fayad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.53,0:35:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He just died.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.71,0:35:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.74,0:35:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-告诉我你找到他了  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tell me you got him. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.15,0:36:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊斯州长和霍斯拉滕议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor Royce and Congresswoman Hookstraten
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.34,0:36:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是美国企业研究所的董事会成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are both on the board of the American Enterprise Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.05,0:36:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有他们能让他回来...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If anyone can get him back to the table...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.88,0:36:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪明  做得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was smart. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.77,0:36:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.62,0:36:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's coming back on the line now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.90,0:36:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢你  -不客气  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - My pleasure, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.95,0:36:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊斯州长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor Royce.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.27,0:36:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找到你还真不容易啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a hard man to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.80,0:36:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前和你说过  我很忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I told you before. I'm pretty busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.80,0:36:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会尽力减轻你的工作量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we're gonna try and lighten the load for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.11,0:36:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郑重声明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the record,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.91,0:36:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在下令  让你手下的警察退下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am ordering you to have your police stand down
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.35,0:36:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止侵扰迪尔伯恩的穆斯林社区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and stop harassing the Muslim community in Dearborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.10,0:36:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且释放\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I also need you to release
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.21,0:36:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有被你们扣押的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}everybody that you've picked up today
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.86,0:36:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没被你正式定罪的民众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you have not formally charged with a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.06,0:36:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉过你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I told you before,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.10,0:36:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的警察们在尽其所能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my police are doing what they have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.15,0:36:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护我的公民们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to protect my citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.43,0:36:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言  州长  他们不是您的公民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With all due respect, Governor, they're not your citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.73,0:36:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是我的  我的职责就是保护他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're mine, and it's my job to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.08,0:36:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本来就不该有这职责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a job you have no business doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.81,0:36:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪法可不这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, not according to the Constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.35,0:36:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,州长  你还应该知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor, you should also know
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.53,0:36:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的警察在不知情情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that your police unknowingly picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.41,0:36:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓了三名为国土安全部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}three undercover operatives
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.86,0:36:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行长期调查任务的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}working on a long lead investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.52,0:36:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卧底探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for Homeland Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.06,0:36:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能告诉你他们的名字  因为这是机密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't give you their names because it's classified,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.44,0:36:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你的安全级别不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you don't have clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.16,0:37:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我要你释放\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is why I need you to release
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.65,0:37:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天抓的所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}everybody that you've picked up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.83,0:37:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会这么做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well... I'm not gonna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.59,0:37:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  州长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, then, Governor,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.24,0:37:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是阻碍联邦调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'll be obstructing a federal investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.11,0:37:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定知道这样做的后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you're aware of the consequences for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.74,0:37:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想保证我的人民安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm just trying to keep my people safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.92,0:37:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早的丹尼·法耶德有多安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How safe is Danny Fayad this evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.73,0:37:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,州长  我现在就要你的回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor, I need your answer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.09,0:37:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给州警打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll call the State Police,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.94,0:37:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们解除警备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tell them to stand down
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.04,0:37:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并释放抓到的所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and release everyone we've picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.99,0:37:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.11,0:37:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  需要我联系国土安全部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, would you like me to contact Homeland Security,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.64,0:37:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知他们的探员已被释放吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tell them their agents have been released?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.45,0:37:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面没有探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were no agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.24,0:37:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是虚张声势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.18,0:37:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,权宜之计  暂时先止止血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A band-aid - to stop the bleeding for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.41,0:37:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.63,0:37:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊斯州长是个好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor Royce is a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.11,0:38:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是今天犯了错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was just wrong today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.60,0:38:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-感谢你的协助  金布尔  -总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you for your help, Kimble. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.39,0:38:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.00,0:38:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.52,0:38:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛斯  你能等一下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth, can you hold up for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.28,0:38:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Walk with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.11,0:38:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特区警察给白宫总机打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}D.C. Police called the White House switchboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.01,0:38:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要确认你在这里工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}wanted to confirm that you worked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.02,0:38:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早晨发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.10,0:38:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和密歇根发生的事一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened in Michigan.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.22,0:38:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一直发生的一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What always happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.23,0:38:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当人们不知道敌人是谁时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When people don't know who their enemy is,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.59,0:38:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就开始向我这样的人发难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they start with people who look like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.37,0:38:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想让我指出阿尔-萨卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They want me to name Al-Sakar
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.00,0:38:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爆炸案的始作俑者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as the group behind the bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.12,0:38:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但联调局不能百分百确认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the FBI can't confirm with absolute certainty
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.31,0:38:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他们做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that they did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.28,0:38:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我什么都不能做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.74,0:38:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则  我就会像罗伊斯州长一样差劲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Otherwise, I'd be just as bad as Governor Royce.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.18,0:38:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要找到真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got to get this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.28,0:39:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.69,0:39:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你怎么回家  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How are you getting home? - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.04,0:39:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you getting home?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.87,0:39:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以让特工处送你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can have the Secret Service drive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.78,0:39:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不必劳烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no. That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.57,0:39:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  总统先生  我没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.26,0:39:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心啊  赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be careful, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.49,0:39:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.68,0:39:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.80,0:39:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wyatt!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.02,0:39:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.09,0:39:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给我丹尼·法耶德父母的电话号码吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could I please have the number for Danny Fayad's parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.44,0:39:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要你们知道  言语无法表达\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to know that words could never express
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.54,0:39:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你们失去亲人的哀悼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how sorry I am for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.20,0:40:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  先生  晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.24,0:40:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}柯克曼国会大厦访问成为灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.28,0:40:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.15,0:40:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会碰巧有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wouldn't happen to have a baseball cap
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.59,0:40:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一顶棒球帽吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}laying around, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.32,0:40:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.95,0:40:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你失去了亲人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lose someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.07,0:40:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.27,0:41:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lost everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.60,0:41:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.83,0:41:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.54,0:41:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.73,0:41:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.24,0:41:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.85,0:41:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}托马斯·亚当·柯克曼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.14,0:41:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}住房与城市发展部的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.70,0:41:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}住房与城市发展部的部长  托马斯·亚当·柯克曼规划部门前景
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.10,0:41:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你带我来这里  麦克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for bringing me here, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.08,0:41:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很荣幸  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an honor, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.01,0:42:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.90,0:42:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里  找到一名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, over here! We found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.08,0:42:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got a survivor!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.76,0:42:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got a survivor over here!

